ming to fine details only\n\n**Getting strange/unexpected outputs?**\n\n- Reduce shift_strength to 50-70%\n- Try a different direction shift pattern\n- Make sure your ComfyUI is up-to-date! "],"color":"#2f9e3f","bgcolor":"#263628"},{"id":71,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-1060,280],"size":[570,580],"flags":{},"order":4,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"RBG Smart Seed Variance 🌱","properties":{},"widgets_values":["## Feature List 🚀\n\n- **7 Intelligent Presets:** Pre-configured variance levels from Subtle to Wild:\n\n  - **🌱 Subtle** - Gentle diversity for fine-tuning\n  - **🌿 Balanced** - Sweet spot for most use cases\n  - **🪴 Creative** - Unlock more artistic variations\n  - **🌳 Bold** - Significant structural changes\n  - **🌴 Wild** - Maximum diversity for exploration (Note this might break your prompt, use with caution!)\n  - **⚙️ Custom** - Fine-tune with percentage slider (0-100%)\n<br>\n- **Model-Specific Optimization:** Automatic adjustment for your architecture:\n\n  - **Krea2, Z-Image Turbo**, **Qwen-Image**, **Flux (Dev/Schnell)**, **Chroma HD, Ernie-Image**, **Wan** and more!\n\n- **25 Direction Shift Patterns:** Apply structured artistic biases instead of pure random noise.\n- **7 Spatial Fade Curves:** Control how noise fades across the embedding space.\n- **Flexible Noise Injection Timing:** Control when variance is applied.\n- **Prompt Token Protection:** Preserve specific parts of your prompt from noise."],"color":"#2a55cf","bgcolor":"#252b3e"},{"id":70,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-470,280],"size":[570,580],"flags":{},"order":5,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"RBG Smart Seed Variance 🌱","properties":{},"widgets_values":["## 💡 Pro Tips\n\n- **Start conservative:** Begin with \"Balanced\" preset and adjust up/down based on results\n- **Experiment with directions:** Each artistic direction creates unique aesthetic shifts - try them all!\n- **Protect your keywords:** Use \"First Half\" protection if important prompt concepts are being overridden\n- **Track your seed:** Use consistent seeds to compare variance effects side-by-side\n- **Model matters:** Always select the correct model type for optimal results and to avoid over-correction\n- **Combine strategies:** Mix direction shifts with fade curves and noise injection timing for sophisticated effects\n- **Use custom mode:** Fine-tune with the slider when presets don't match your needs exactly\n- **Chain more than one:** For advanced effects, you can chain multiple Smart Seed Variance nodes.\n- **Share settings with the Community:** If you find a killer setting combination Export them and share with the open-source community.\n"],"color":"#9e3fc0","bgcolor":"#36283b"},{"id":67,"type":"RBG_Smart_Seed_Variance","pos":[510,910],"size":[300,428],"flags":{"pinned":true},"order":10,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"conditioning","name":"conditioning","type":"CONDITIONING","link":69},{"localized_name":"target_vibe","name":"target_vibe","shape":7,"type":"CONDITIONING","link":null},{"localized_name":"variance_preset","name":"variance_preset","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"variance_preset"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"fine_tune_variance","name":"fine_tune_variance","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"fine_tune_variance"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"model_type","name":"model_type","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"model_type"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"fade_curve","name":"fade_curve","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"fade_curve"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"noise_injection","name":"noise_injection","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"noise_injection"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"protect_mode","name":"protect_mode","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"protect_mode"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"protect_regions","name":"protect_regions","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"protect_regions"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"direction_shift","name":"direction_shift","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"direction_shift"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"s